desc: Take your Cricut crafting to the next level with these gorgeous 3D layered mandala SVGs for Cricut, Silhouette and other cutting machines. SVG, PNG & SilhouetteDXF file formats included.

layout.text:
A unique collection of 3D papercraft SVG files to cut with your Cricut, Silhouette or ScanNCut machine.

Over 500 layered SVGs to choose from, for every occasion.
